{"tid":958890,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉拍《大帥哥》足證香港人唔配有新免費電視台","createTime":"2018-12-28T07:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T11:42:25.000Z","uid":57405,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46a3a42edd29696cc4f6e4772d75dfd13abcc6ae","tid":958890,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:38:04.000Z","msg":"張偉健返CCTVB拍《大帥哥》，又令到班成日話要抵制CCTVB既「港豬」起哂哄<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其中有一個角色冬來，成班連登仔女日捧夜捧。<br />\n人地當日係CCTVB成日做死人，之後過HKTV雖然冇主角做，但起碼係《警界線》做啞仔都叫做有代表性，反而冇人報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n而家人地返CCTVB終於唔洗死，你班連登仔女同傳媒就日吹夜吹捧人，又話咩終於出人頭地云云<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明人地有機會係HKTV拍功夫片，就係因為689玩野唔發牌先冇發圍機會。<br />\n所以話，香港電視業之死唔係因為689同中共，係死係連登仔女同香港人本身，成日話CCTVB點衰點衰，成日叫人唔睇，但大家又成日開Post討論，其他台有口裨既節目又唔見咁多人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"1cdd3d2a1391a7c1dc89e794862df758cc51355a","tid":958890,"uid":179967,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:09:54.000Z","msg":"第一日識香港人?<br />\n同埋依家連登根本有好多都蝗種黎"},{"pid":"66b0cc4813de11dc5ffab5b98934adcbd79254ec","tid":958890,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T11:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}